.SH NAME
splice_from_pipe_begin \- start splicing from pipe
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" splice_from_pipe_begin
.BI "(struct splice_desc *sd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sd" 12
information about the splice operation
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function should be called before a loop containing
\fBsplice_from_pipe_next\fP and \fBsplice_from_pipe_feed\fP to
initialize the necessary fields of \fIsd\fP.
